org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.SAM

Interface SaStep

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GaScenario, GaStep, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceUsage, TimedElement, TimedProcessing
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SaStepImpl

    public interface SaStep
extends GaStep
    A representation of the model object 'Sa Step'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Behavioral Feature
    • Deadline
    • Spare Cap
    • Sch Slack
    • Preempt T
    • Ready T
    • Nonpreemption Blocking
    • Shared Res
    • Self Suspension Blocking
    • Number Self Suspensions
    See Also:
    SAMPackage.getSaStep()
